{"tid":257174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身為臺灣人很欣賞香港的口語字在網路世界能相當程度文字化","createTime":"2017-05-25T05:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T13:38:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e367d38e7866d985b9d2c7573e87a9ee3ef8dba5","tid":257174,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"身為臺灣人很欣賞香港的口語字在網路世界能相當程度文字化，臺灣目前的正體字只限於國語，在臺語運用上是比較各行其是的走不同的系統<br />\n這一點我這臺語使用者希望未來能像粵語使用者毫無困難的用電腦、電話在網路世界傳達溝通臺語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lt;iframe src=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155247748232357&amp;width=500&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fcheng.lap.9%252Fposts%252F10155247748232357%26width%3D500%22&d=Nfmd4bDsoH5erfxcdPPtTQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0e7f482e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155247748232357&amp;width=500&quot;</a> width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;257&quot; style=&quot;border:none;overflow:hidden&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowTransparency=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;"},{"pid":"3a80a6d9f45a2e003f1935da80004cb408006387","tid":257174,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:16:06.000Z","msg":"[url]&lt;iframe src=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155247748232357&amp;width=500&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fcheng.lap.9%252Fposts%252F10155247748232357%26width%3D500%22&d=Nfmd4bDsoH5erfxcdPPtTQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0e7f482e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155247748232357&amp;width=500&quot;</a> width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;257&quot; style=&quot;border:none;overflow:hidden&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowTransparency=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;[/url]"},{"pid":"a4bf3780285ee673c03ef19f876b32c82f28afb7","tid":257174,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:18:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155247748232357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155247748232357&d=Nfmd4bDsoH5erfxcdPPtTQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7dc0c040\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155247748232357</a>"},{"pid":"9966810171b436785626eaaa3f9e8f6bd0aa205c","tid":257174,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa12b48c3ea1f75838260637637644d626f48b7e","tid":257174,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"台語唔係中華民國語言，台灣人是用國語的𠂆𠂆<br />\n台灣人才不是台客𠂆𠂆"},{"pid":"2f6a440d31425615899150e9bd9549f60ecbe282","tid":257174,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"我們每天都在用噢"},{"pid":"22e01256ee3770fee72b2dec78b5722d72bec948","tid":257174,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我們每天都在用噢</blockquote><br />\n靠腰喔，真坑爹，傻B的香港人，台灣人根本每天都在用囉 𠂆𠂆<br />\n台灣都用 未聽過嗎？𠂆𠂆"},{"pid":"1082c8f1f9074245b951526d6d06a9f51ed8a15c","tid":257174,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:04:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我們每天都在用噢</blockquote><br />\n靠腰喔，真坑爹，傻B的香港人，台灣人根本每天都在用囉 𠂆𠂆<br />\n台灣都用 未聽過嗎？𠂆𠂆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n版大你說的是支那普通話吧？<br />\n我們會說靠夭<br />\n但不會講坑爹傻b這種支那話噢<br />\n以上"},{"pid":"33f29319e17ad5d3e8662085de7c29bb2cd7a245","tid":257174,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我們每天都在用噢</blockquote><br />\n靠腰喔，真坑爹，傻B的香港人，台灣人根本每天都在用囉 𠂆𠂆<br />\n台灣都用 未聽過嗎？𠂆𠂆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n版大你說的是支那普通話吧？<br />\n我們會說靠夭<br />\n但不會講坑爹傻b這種支那話噢<br />\n以上</blockquote><br />\n𠂆𠂆，真的假的？！<br />\n但是香港人滿愛用「台灣都用」來說不是蝗語喔"},{"pid":"299aee57e68afc1f74346956a9b823d14c74db42","tid":257174,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"一句「屌你老母」已經威震八方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26a535817f9e427e511f26d4cba76dd294edb3e","tid":257174,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:16:48.000Z","msg":"睇唔明佢段野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56e479c33a7bda81e7a180b7309c47afbf8defd","tid":257174,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:25:01.000Z","msg":"其實注音文好似只係另一種寫法嘅中文併音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上都只係中文而唔係台語入文"},{"pid":"6cf80f8c68d3ca8a0cdc75c0ae1c75f3db2c30f7","tid":257174,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"第三世界咁"},{"pid":"ab176ecd1b441046e673444879585987f3e1b6ae","tid":257174,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實注音文好似只係另一種寫法嘅中文併音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上都只係中文而唔係台語入文</blockquote><br />\n睇你點睇<br />\n全世界說大部分都拼音文字，得漢字唔係（好似係）<br />\n所以拼音唔係語言唔係入文係講唔過，泡都係用拼音嚟入文（洽唔洽當就另外嘅話題）<br />\n只係台灣人真係唔多用台語呢，至少台北唔係"},{"pid":"b7104f5e450b87299a6887156a8ebf3b0b7807bd","tid":257174,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實注音文好似只係另一種寫法嘅中文併音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上都只係中文而唔係台語入文</blockquote><br />\n睇你點睇<br />\n全世界說大部分都拼音文字，得漢字唔係（好似係）<br />\n所以拼音唔係語言唔係入文係講唔過，泡都係用拼音嚟入文（洽唔洽當就另外嘅話題）<br />\n只係台灣人真係唔多用台語呢，至少台北唔係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思佢地用注音文但係成句都係一般中文文法同詞語 (最多係口語化少少)<br />\n變相其實只係「用非漢字打中文」而唔係「台語入文」"},{"pid":"5c4544ad7465c5b11aa783a66009f0491caf0a15","tid":257174,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實注音文好似只係另一種寫法嘅中文併音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上都只係中文而唔係台語入文</blockquote><br />\n睇你點睇<br />\n全世界說大部分都拼音文字，得漢字唔係（好似係）<br />\n所以拼音唔係語言唔係入文係講唔過，泡都係用拼音嚟入文（洽唔洽當就另外嘅話題）<br />\n只係台灣人真係唔多用台語呢，至少台北唔係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思佢地用注音文但係成句都係一般中文文法同詞語 (最多係口語化少少)<br />\n變相其實只係「用非漢字打中文」而唔係「台語入文」</blockquote><br />\n咪就係因為佢地台語唔常用囉<br />\n佢地有心可以用注音打台語，只係佢地根本唔常用"}]}